Osoit oishu o losho osinya


1  Enturrai elap pooki, o losek, o esunkureisho o esukeny pooki, nitiuwu anaa inkera naanana, 
2  entang'uar ororei le Nkiyang'et nemeeta olosek, paa te ninye ibululu aabaiki enjeunoto. 
3   Amu inchiamishama enanai e oshoke o Laitoriani. 
4  Wootu enetii ninye, osoit otanyaita iltung'ana, kake etegeluaki, neeta tipat too nkonyek e Enkai. 
5  Anaa isoito ooishu, pee iakuku inkasisin e mumuaisho sinyati ooitayu ilasarri sinyat le Nkiyang'et oong'uarrayu te Enkai te Yesu Kristo. 
6   Amu etisiraki ti atua Ilkigerot aajo,

“Ng'ura airragie te Sion Osoit kitok lo lmairroto,

ogeluno negol enkinyiang'a,

ore pooki oiruk nemeitukurruni.”


7   Ore te intae ilooiruk keeta tipat oleng, kake ore te lelo lemeiruk, etaa “Ilo soit otanyaita ilashetak otaa kitok to lmairroto” 
8   naa “Osoit orror iltung'ana, osoit sapuk obatat iltung'ana,” errorro ninche amu etanyaita ening ororei, naa ina apake eitaanyaki ninche.


9   Irara intae olorere ogeluno, inkasisin e nkaji e nkitoo, olorere sinyati, iltung'ana le Enkai makewan, pee itumutumu aainosai inkiaasin enyena e nking'asia, oloipotuo intae entung'uai enaimin aitijing atua ewang'an enye naing'asiasho. 
10   Intae ilemera olorere apa; kake irara taata olorere le Enkai Ileitu apa etum olng'ur kake itang'amutua olng'ur.

Isinkan le Nkai


11  Ilanyor laainei asai intae, anaa ilomon o laisikak pee ipaasharere ing'uarrat o sesen naashet enjore naarare iltauja linyi. 
12  Niaakuku ilooata orrekie sidai ti atua Loreren lemeiruk, pee te neiro neiteleiki intae mbaa anaa laasak loo ntorrok, neidim te nedol too nkiasin inyi sidain, aaisisa Enkai te nkolong e muta.


13  Eyanyita pooki kitoria oo ltung'ana to lbae lo Laitoriani, te naa ko laiguanani kitok, 
14  anaa ilooti te ninye ooirriwuaki meitamio lelo ooas intorrok neisis lelo ooas isidain. 
15  Amu eyieunoto e Enkai inchere ore te yasata oo sidain nintigiriri emodai oo ltung'ana oomoda. 
16  Entotoni anaa iltung'ana oolakuno, nimintaa elakunoto inyi entoki nintiemorierie entorroni, kake entobik anaa ilaisiaayiak le Enkai. 
17  Eyanyita iltung'ana pooki, entonyor ilalashera, entureita olaiguanani kitok.

Enkitanyaanyukoto o sina le Kristo


18  Lo aisiaayiak entadou ate, niyanyititi oleng ilaitoriak linyi, neme ake isupati nebor, kake o metabaiki lelo ooisomit intae. 
19  Amu keishori oltung'ani enchunet te naa, ore nkaraki nadamu Enkai neng'iri te neidong'i metii esipata. 
20  Amu kaa dupoto ina, te neitamei intae enkata niaasiasa intorrok? Kake te niaasiasa isupati, ning'iriri te neisilisili intae niaatata enchunet te Enkai. 
21  Amu te ina eipotoki intae, amu eisilisiloki sii ninye Kristo te nkaraki intae, neing'ueki intae enkitanyaanyukoto, pee isujusuju iroruat enyena. 
22   Eitu eas ninye eng'oki, neitu etumieki te nkutuk enye ororei lo losek laa ore pee emori, 
23   neitu eshukoki emorisho, ore pee e isilisili neitu ejo aarisho, kake eitarasaka imbaa enyena pooki ilo oiguenare te sipata. 
24   Ninye makewan otanapa ing'ok ang to sesen lenye te shumata olchani, pee kitum aatuata too ng'ok, neaku aikinchu too supati, too lbaa lenyena eishiunyieki intae. 
25   Amu itapong'ori anaa intare naaimina, kake itorrinyokinote taata Olchekut naa Olaing'urani loo ltauja linyi.

